Nigerian social media big boy and self-styled celebrity barman, Cubana Chief Priest, has finally been released from police custody. The celebrity barman was detained for allegedly misusing police escorts and also to answer questions about his ‘unexplained wealth’. Insiders allege that a jealous friend set him up to be investigated for his extravagant lifestyle. READ ALSO PDP condemns arrest of CUPP Spokesman, Ugochinyere Anyways, Cubana took to his social media to show fans that he has now been released.